languages.text: Возрождению искалеченного Веабоса-6 положено начало. На астропатический зов прибудут сотни техножрецов и тысячи паломников Омниссии. Вместе, пропевая арии реконструкции и перезапуска, они очистят атмосферу, восстановят экстракциумы и залечат раны их духов машин. Но путь этот будет долог и затратен для династии фон Валанциус.

languages.text: The restoration of the crippled Vheabos VI has begun. Hundreds of Tech-Priests and thousands of the Omnissiah's pilgrims will answer the Astropathic call. Together, singing the litanies of reconstruction and re-ignition, they will purify the atmosphere, restore the extractiums, and heal the wounds of their machine spirits. But this path will be long and costly for the von Valancius dynasty.

traits.locale_text: The restoration of the crippled Vheabos VI has begun. Hundreds of Tech-Priests and thousands of Omnissiah pilgrims will answer the astropathic call. Together, singing the lithanies of reconstruction and reboot, they will purify the atmosphere, restore the extractiums and heal the wounds of their machine spirits. But this path will be long and costly for the von Valanсius dynasty.
